Popular entertainer cum good governance activist, Charles Oputa, has confirmed that he sustained injury from a scooter accident. The ‘Area Fada’, who made this known on his Twitter page said the incident occurred on Tuesday night. Sharing images of his wounded face, the 70-year-old appreciated God for quick healing and thanked those who sympathized with him . ”See as I go fall on top my scooter Scatter my face. Thank God I’m healing. I hit the road today. ”All those wey SORRY for me God bless una. ”All those wey yab me, dey call me Agbaya, biko allow me catch my cruise jare!” he added. We considered surrogacy after many failed IVF – Banky W 